         (aud.logoff$time IS NOT NULL AND aud.logoff$time > cast(:2 as DATE)) 
         ORDER BY aud.ntimestamp# ,aud.logoff$time
   Rationale
      The SQL spent 100% of its database time on CPU, I/O and Cluster waits. 
      This part of database time may be improved by the SQL Tuning Advisor.
   Rationale
      Database time for this SQL was divided as follows: 100% for SQL 
      execution, 0% for parsing, 0% for PL/SQL execution and 0% for Java 
      execution.
   Rationale
      SQL statement with SQL_ID "g5ksxj58a9x0h" was executed 19 times and had 
      an average elapsed time of 90 seconds.

Impact is .73 active sessions, 2.35% of total activity.
-------------------------------------------------------

significant database time.
 
   Recommendation 1: Application Analysis
   Estimated benefit is .73 active sessions, 2.35% of total activity.
